---
title: Familia Chilli Con Carne with Basmati Rice, Avo and Soured Cream
description: Sombreros at the ready, here comes chilli con carne with all the extras! Beef mince, kidney beans and tomatoes in a warm spicy sauce all the family will love. Have it your way topped with sour cream, grated cheese, a little guacamole, extra chilli - the choice is yours.
